    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text> A tertiary alcohol found in linaloe oil and other essential oils. It is used in perfumery and is a common component of flower odors. In conservation, it is used as a mild antifungal agent on paper, silver photographs, and leather.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
